track.name: Running on Faith
comments: 'oldstonersrock' brings back memories of the decades old debate of 'who' is the best guitarist. With virtuoso players such as; Alvin Lee, Gary Moore, Rory Gallagher, Jeff Beck, Jimmy Page, the Kings, John Mayall, Buddy Guy and --- I know I left a few out, it is a pretty hard pick. But my pick is definitely the Supreme Axer. And that is Jimmy Hendrix! I saw him live way back when at the Civic Opera House in Chicago. Nobody could touch him. What a Talent! To bad he left us so soon before he could really reach his full potential.
